Package dataanalyzer.listeners

Contains listeners used by the algorithm system.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
CompletionListener A listener to signal that a operation has been complete.
OutputListener Used by AlgorithmProcess to signal listeners that new Output has been created.
ProcessListener Used by an AlgorithmProcess to signal that the AlgorithmProcess wants to create another AlgorithmProcess.
ProgressListener Listens for progress updates for an operation.
SystemListener used by UserInterface objects to assioate an Object waiting to collect another Object from the UserInterface.
